data.description: An OO interface to the Nagios command pipe.
data.PS: The following links are only valid for module list maintainers:
data.rationale:
The Nagios:: namespace should already have been accepted as of May
    29, 2003. I believe Stanley Hopcroft
    (stanley.hopcroft@ipaustralia.gov.au) was the person who requested
    this. This is the first in a series of modules for interfacing with
    Nagios (http://www.nagios.org) that I will be submitting.
